{"tid":631640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國中興通訊 對英國國家安全造成威脅","createTime":"2018-04-16T15:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T01:35:10.000Z","uid":4783,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"db44788190f3f6e6802ee8b2f928e8e516c89d37","tid":631640,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"37 minutes ago<br />\n<br />\n國家網路安全中心警告國內電訊商使用中國中興通訊設備和服務會對國家安全造成威脅<br />\n<br />\nThe National Cyber Security Centre (NCSC) has written to UK telecoms providers warning them that the use of ZTE's equipment and services could pose a national security risk.<br />\n<br />\n此舉與美國政府禁止美國企業售賣電子零件到中國深圳的公司吻合<br />\n<br />\nThe move coincides with a US government ban preventing American businesses from selling components to the Shenzhen-based company.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;It is entirely appropriate and part of NCSC's duty to highlight potential risks to the UK's national security and provide advice based on our technical expertise,&quot; said a statement from Dr Ian Levy, the organisation's technical director.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;NCSC assess that the national security risks arising from the use of ZTE equipment or services within the context of the existing UK telecommunications infrastructure cannot be mitigated.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The UK telecommunications network already contains a significant amount of equipment supplied by Huawei, also a Chinese equipment manufacturer,&quot; he wrote.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Adding in new equipment and services from another Chinese supplier would render our existing mitigations ineffective.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe NCSC's parent organisation, GCHQ, already carries out its own checks on Huawei's equipment.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Sanctions buster</ins></strong><br />\nThe US's action against ZTE stems from the fact the firm sold on US hardware and software to an Iranian telecoms carrier, in breach of sanctions imposed by Washington.<br />\n<br />\nZTE pleaded guilty to the offence last year and paid a $890m (&pound;621m) penalty.<br />\n<br />\nAt the time the firm also promised to dismiss four senior workers and discipline 35 others. But it acknowledged in March that while it had fired the four managers, it had failed to keep the second part of its promise.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We can't trust what they are telling us is truthful,&quot; a unnamed US official told the Reuters news agency.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;And in international commerce, truth is pretty important.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-43784990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-43784990&d=I72V8AtZztMkIY0Z8oawy8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=54349e32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-43784990&h=8a938e44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-43784990</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開始了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0741fb307c261d92b6b93dbbd7c64ab4838479ed","tid":631640,"uid":76879,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T15:48:24.000Z","msg":"前排個叔父仲叫我763 28蚊<br />\n好抵快D大手入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d494a9a963a9263b19f89ee734e037a7d31df4b7","tid":631640,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T16:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d9ebc42cacc1f362b16e5072d0c464f7e20720","tid":631640,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"美商務部下殺手鐧 禁出口中興通訊敏感技術<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/631676/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/631676/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n英美又合作了<img src=\"/assets/face